Bracer (20% parsed) = 1120 * 0.2 = 224<br>
Extra Crit Damage = (at 50%) = 1120 * 0.5 =560<br>
                            (at 54%) = 1120 * 0.54 = 604.8<br>
                            (at 55%) = 1120 * 0.55 = 616<br>
--------------------------------------------------<br>
First total = 1904<br>
